    • Method Detail

      • getInstance

        public static Cargo getInstance()
        Returns a static instance of the Cargo subsystem. If none has been created yet, the instance is created. This enables multiple other subsystems and any other classes to use this class without having to pass an instance or take the risk of trying to instantiate multiple instances of this class, which would result in errors.
        Returns:
        a static instance of the Cargo subsystem.
